WEBVTT

00:01.080 --> 00:02.040
Return to the capital

00:02.800 --> 00:04.320
And properly meet

00:04.320 --> 00:06.600
Our Great Xuan's first female official

00:11.960 --> 00:12.680
You smiled

00:16.560 --> 00:17.560
All these years

00:18.200 --> 00:20.400
I've rarely seen you truly smile

00:25.320 --> 00:26.200
Your Majesty

00:38.520 --> 00:41.400
To be able to treat Your Majesty as an equal

00:42.520 --> 00:43.760
And grow old together

00:44.880 --> 00:46.160
Is Wan'er's fortune
